I did save your life, you know.

5
00:00:29,760 --> 00:00:30,800
Don't I get something in return?

6
00:00:40,119 --> 00:00:40,679
Oh, please.

7
00:00:42,079 --> 00:00:44,159
Go kill yourself now, I won't stop you.

8
00:00:49,000 --> 00:00:50,240
You said you saved me.

9
00:00:50,840 --> 00:00:52,200
Then my life belongs to you.

10
00:00:52,399 --> 00:00:53,719
You want to be my woman?

11
00:00:54,039 --> 00:00:55,039
You'd better not regret it.

12
00:00:55,159 --> 00:00:56,280
I'm not even afraid of death.

13
00:00:56,920 --> 00:00:57,840
How could I ever regret this?

14
00:01:58,920 --> 00:01:59,439
Siqi.

15
00:01:59,879 --> 00:02:00,519
What are you doing?

16
00:02:05,439 --> 00:02:06,319
Ignoring me again?

17
00:02:09,120 --> 00:02:09,560
Hey.

18
00:02:10,639 --> 00:02:11,400
You...

19
00:02:12,479 --> 00:02:13,680
Can you stay and chat for a bit?

20
00:02:14,039 --> 00:02:14,719
Right now?

21
00:02:15,360 --> 00:02:15,759
Yeah.

22
00:02:16,639 --> 00:02:17,159
Okay.

23
00:02:19,719 --> 00:02:22,120
But I have to take these to the kitchen.

24
00:02:22,639 --> 00:02:23,520
Wait for me a sec.

25
00:02:24,080 --> 00:02:24,599
I'll be quick.

26
00:02:25,159 --> 00:02:25,840
Wait for me.

27
00:02:28,680 --> 00:02:30,080
Watch the cart, coming through.

28
00:02:32,520 --> 00:02:34,199
When I could no longer dance,

29
00:02:34,919 --> 00:02:36,120
I lost all faith

30
00:02:36,400 --> 00:02:37,719
in this world.

31
00:02:38,759 --> 00:02:40,560
I felt my life had no value.

32
00:02:41,840 --> 00:02:42,759
Until I met him.

33
00:02:46,879 --> 00:02:48,479
Downstream is the sewage zone.

34
00:02:48,919 --> 00:02:50,599
The smell won't be too pleasant.

35
00:02:56,520 --> 00:02:57,520
What are you staring at?

36
00:02:57,680 --> 00:02:59,039
I did save your life, you know.

37
00:03:00,240 --> 00:03:01,240
Don't I get something in return?

38
00:03:10,520 --> 00:03:11,319
Oh, please.

39
00:03:12,400 --> 00:03:14,520
Go kill yourself now, I won't stop you.

40
00:03:19,400 --> 00:03:20,520
You said you saved me.

41
00:03:21,280 --> 00:03:22,560
Then my life belongs to you.

42
00:03:22,840 --> 00:03:24,280
You want to be my woman?

43
00:03:24,439 --> 00:03:25,360
You'd better not regret it.

44
00:03:25,680 --> 00:03:26,879
I'm not even afraid of death.

45
00:03:27,400 --> 00:03:28,240
How could I ever regret this?

46
00:03:46,719 --> 00:03:47,520
He said,

47
00:03:49,439 --> 00:03:50,800
"I'm a lonely wind,

48
00:03:51,719 --> 00:03:53,159
drifting across the wasteland."

49
00:03:54,520 --> 00:03:55,199
I felt

50
00:03:57,199 --> 00:03:58,400
he was the one who understood me most.

51
00:04:05,520 --> 00:04:07,520
Boss Bai has fallen this low?

52
00:04:08,120 --> 00:04:09,680
What a waste of our time.

53
00:04:09,879 --> 00:04:10,479
Chen Hui.

54
00:04:10,759 --> 00:04:12,000
The heat is so intense out there,

55
00:04:12,000 --> 00:04:13,159
and we're still going after Yu Tianfang?

56
00:04:13,240 --> 00:04:15,120
The cops all think I'll run.

57
00:04:15,319 --> 00:04:17,399
I'm going to do the exact opposite.

58
00:04:17,399 --> 00:04:19,240
Catch them all completely off guard.

59
00:04:22,399 --> 00:04:22,800
Chen Hui.

60
00:04:34,680 --> 00:04:35,600
Chen Hui and Ma Xiaojun

61
00:04:36,079 --> 00:04:37,439
likely fled in this direction.

62
00:04:50,920 --> 00:04:51,720
Yu Tianfang.

63
00:04:54,680 --> 00:04:56,079
We finally meet.

64
00:04:56,720 --> 00:04:57,639
Chen Hui, huh?

65
00:04:58,240 --> 00:04:59,439
Just you?

66
00:04:59,720 --> 00:05:00,720
Let me tell you,

67
00:05:00,920 --> 00:05:02,959
calling you "old man" is being generous.

68
00:05:03,240 --> 00:05:04,639
At your age,

69
00:05:04,639 --> 00:05:05,959
toying with a young girl's feelings,

70
00:05:05,959 --> 00:05:07,319
have you no shame?

71
00:05:07,680 --> 00:05:08,639
Why you...

72
00:05:08,800 --> 00:05:09,759
I dodge,

73
00:05:11,160 --> 00:05:11,759
I duck,

74
00:05:12,160 --> 00:05:13,120
I weave.

75
00:05:21,519 --> 00:05:22,600
Touch my woman,

76
00:05:22,959 --> 00:05:24,160
and you pay the price.

77
00:05:24,399 --> 00:05:25,879
Want to lose a leg,

78
00:05:26,639 --> 00:05:28,079
or lose an arm?

79
00:05:28,079 --> 00:05:29,160
Screw you, you bastard!

80
00:05:30,399 --> 00:05:31,160
Put the gun down!

81
00:05:31,959 --> 00:05:32,639
Drop the gun!

82
00:05:40,240 --> 00:05:41,600
Chu Feng, Chen Hui got away!

83
00:05:43,920 --> 00:05:44,519
Don't move!

84
00:05:47,480 --> 00:05:48,040
Watch out!

85
00:05:57,639 --> 00:05:58,199
Watch out!

86
00:06:01,839 --> 00:06:02,399
Cuff him.

87
00:06:06,759 --> 00:06:07,439
Behave yourself.

88
00:06:16,680 --> 00:06:17,240
Stop right there!

89
00:06:33,879 --> 00:06:34,439
Stop!

90
00:06:43,800 --> 00:06:44,360
Chen Dahui!

91
00:06:45,920 --> 00:06:46,680
You can't escape!

92
00:06:47,120 --> 00:06:48,279
Even if I die,

93
00:06:48,279 --> 00:06:50,000
I won't let you succeed!

94
00:06:55,199 --> 00:06:55,639
Stop!

95
00:07:16,399 --> 00:07:17,920
Let's go to hell together!

96
00:07:42,879 --> 00:07:43,319
Hurry!

97
00:07:47,560 --> 00:07:48,079
Captain Chu.

98
00:07:49,079 --> 00:07:50,199
Behave yourself.

99
00:07:52,199 --> 00:07:52,680
Get in.

100
00:07:54,879 --> 00:07:55,560
Quick, open the door.

101
00:07:57,120 --> 00:07:57,519
Captain.

102
00:07:57,879 --> 00:07:58,360
Are you okay?

103
00:08:00,240 --> 00:08:00,759
Get in, fast.

104
00:08:03,160 --> 00:08:03,759
Behave yourself.

105
00:08:04,040 --> 00:08:05,439
Look at that long face.

106
00:08:05,839 --> 00:08:07,279
Didn't catch him, did you?

107
00:08:08,199 --> 00:08:09,120
That bastard.

108
00:08:09,120 --> 00:08:10,680
Why doesn't heaven just strike him down?

109
00:08:11,319 --> 00:08:12,439
Ma Xiaojun and Chen Hui,

110
00:08:12,439 --> 00:08:13,600
both have blood on their hands.

111
00:08:14,279 --> 00:08:15,319
You must be careful from now on.

112
00:08:16,279 --> 00:08:17,879
Let me make this clear right now.

113
00:08:18,399 --> 00:08:19,720
Even if they don't come after me,

114
00:08:19,720 --> 00:08:21,199
I'll be going after them.

115
00:08:21,519 --> 00:08:22,759
Boss Bai was so good to me,

116
00:08:23,600 --> 00:08:24,879
yet they killed him.

117
00:08:25,639 --> 00:08:27,199
Qibao's still lying in the hospital.

118
00:08:27,199 --> 00:08:28,720
If I don't do something for them, I...

119
00:08:30,040 --> 00:08:31,399
Acting on impulse won't solve anything.

120
00:08:32,480 --> 00:08:34,320
Spend more time with Siqi.

121
00:08:35,120 --> 00:08:36,879
Leave the rest to us.

122
00:08:50,919 --> 00:08:52,240
The restaurant's shut down.

123
00:08:54,240 --> 00:08:55,679
The old crew has all scattered.

124
00:08:57,919 --> 00:08:58,759
But Boss Bai,

125
00:08:59,559 --> 00:09:00,440
don't worry.

126
00:09:01,279 --> 00:09:02,840
I'll definitely keep Qibao safe.

127
00:09:13,159 --> 00:09:13,639
Take him back.

128
00:09:13,919 --> 00:09:14,440
Get out.

129
00:09:19,440 --> 00:09:19,919
What are you doing?

130
00:09:21,200 --> 00:09:21,759
What are you doing?

131
00:09:21,879 --> 00:09:22,440
What are you doing?

132
00:09:22,720 --> 00:09:24,080
Spit it out! Spit!

133
00:09:27,320 --> 00:09:28,360
Go call an ambulance.

134
00:09:28,600 --> 00:09:28,840
Hurry!

135
00:09:28,840 --> 00:09:29,559
I won.

136
00:09:31,679 --> 00:09:32,960
You'd better not regret it.

137
00:09:33,399 --> 00:09:34,879
Because I'm a born bad seed.

138
00:09:35,399 --> 00:09:37,000
Never be too merciful to me.

139
00:09:38,200 --> 00:09:38,919
Where's the ambulance?

140
00:09:40,960 --> 00:09:43,120
Even my own father wanted me dead.

141
00:09:43,120 --> 00:09:43,799
Come quick! Come quick!

142
00:09:45,279 --> 00:09:45,799
Hold him down.

143
00:10:01,879 --> 00:10:02,320
Captain Chu.

144
00:10:02,960 --> 00:10:04,159
The chief wants you back for a meeting.

145
00:10:04,440 --> 00:10:05,919
Captain, the bureau has so much going on.

146
00:10:06,399 --> 00:10:07,159
Head back first.

147
00:10:07,440 --> 00:10:08,240
I'll keep an eye on things here.

148
00:10:10,200 --> 00:10:10,679
Alright.

149
00:10:11,159 --> 00:10:11,759
Keep a close watch.

150
00:10:11,759 --> 00:10:12,559
Got it.

151
00:10:12,720 --> 00:10:13,279
Don't worry.

152
00:10:35,279 --> 00:10:37,080
We've removed the button,

153
00:10:37,240 --> 00:10:38,320
but his stomach is bleeding.

154
00:10:38,320 --> 00:10:39,480
He needs to be hospitalized.

155
00:10:39,480 --> 00:10:40,399
When will he wake up?

156
00:10:41,159 --> 00:10:42,679
Once the anesthesia wears off,

157
00:10:42,679 --> 00:10:43,519
he'll come around.

158
00:10:43,879 --> 00:10:45,039
Take a break if you're tired.

159
00:10:45,559 --> 00:10:46,159
I'm fine.

160
00:10:46,799 --> 00:10:48,399
Times like this call for extra vigilance.

161
00:10:48,720 --> 00:10:49,120
Alright.

162
00:10:57,799 --> 00:10:58,200
Xiao Wang.

163
00:10:58,799 --> 00:10:59,919
Stand guard at the elevator.

164
00:10:59,919 --> 00:11:01,279
Don't let any suspicious person slip by.

165
00:11:01,279 --> 00:11:01,960
Yes, sir.

166
00:11:02,200 --> 00:11:02,600
Lao Zhang,

167
00:11:03,799 --> 00:11:04,600
guard the door.

168
00:11:30,080 --> 00:11:30,960
Are you holding up okay?

169
00:11:31,279 --> 00:11:32,039
Piece of cake.

170
00:11:39,639 --> 00:11:41,360
The cops are watching my every move.

171
00:11:41,759 --> 00:11:42,759
If you want to run,

172
00:11:43,440 --> 00:11:44,399
I'll help you.

173
00:11:45,159 --> 00:11:47,120
Going down with me isn't worth it.

174
00:11:47,639 --> 00:11:48,240
Chen Hui.

175
00:11:48,759 --> 00:11:50,000
It's all that bastard Yu Tianfang's fault,

176
00:11:50,000 --> 00:11:51,240
luring the cops here

177
00:11:51,639 --> 00:11:52,919
and leaving us in this mess.

178
00:11:53,080 --> 00:11:54,399
I can't just let this go.

179
00:11:55,919 --> 00:11:56,879
I was right about you.

180
00:11:59,960 --> 00:12:00,840
If I had no guts,

181
00:12:01,240 --> 00:12:02,320
you wouldn't have saved me.
